Int2LongOpenHash.Int2LongOpenLRUMap

public Int2LongOpenHash.Int2LongOpenLRUMap(int init,
                                           int limit)
growFactor is limit / init. This semantics means expansion occourrs at most once when more than 75% of rooms are filled.
